A RESOLUTION
1 Honoring the Food Bank of Northeast Georgia for its mission of connecting neighbors with
2 nourishing food, its expansion to better serve communities across Northeast Georgia, and its
3 ongoing contributions to economic stability, workforce development, and community
4 well-being; and for other purposes.
5 WHEREAS, a thriving workforce, strong families, and a resilient economy all rely on access
6 to nutritious food, ensuring that Georgians can learn, work, and contribute to their
7 communities without the burden of food insecurity; and
8 WHEREAS, the Food Bank of Northeast Georgia has been a beacon of hope and provision
9 for families across the region, distributing over 15.5 million pounds in 2024 across its
10 15-county service area, reinforcing the importance of community-based solutions to food
11 insecurity; and
12 WHEREAS, through deep-rooted partnerships with Georgia's farmers, businesses,
13 faith-based organizations, nonprofits, and local leaders, the Food Bank of Northeast Georgia
14 transforms every dollar into real impact, leveraging resources to serve those in need with
15 compassion, dignity, and efficacy; and
