39 solutions.
40 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the members of this body recognize the vital role food
41 security plays in ensuring Georgia remains a place where every family has the opportunity
42 to thrive and express their support for efforts that uphold the well-being of Georgia's
43 families, veterans, seniors, and children.
44 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
45 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
46 Food Bank of Northeast Georgia.
